@0 = ~你的谎言越来越令人厌烦了。如果这个“兜帽人”是罪魁祸首，那我们为什么会找到你而不是他？~
@1 = ~他是个法师，而且是一个非常强大的法师。他可能对我们所有人都施加了一些幻术。~
@2 = ~Because I was framed, you fool! Belt himself said that some powerful magics were used to obscure the truth of what had happened. Tell me, is he lying as well?~
@4 = ~上尉，你在做什么？~
@5 = ~No—no! She has to die! Die in the name of Skie Silvershield! Kill her!~
@6 = ~No—no! He has to die! Die in the name of Skie Silvershield! Kill him!~